        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="panoPopup controls">
      	<span class="icon gear"></span><span class="link icon lock"></span><br />
      	<span title="Benachbarte Panoramen" class="link icon camera"></span>
      	<span title="Info Links" class="link icon text"></span>
      	<span title="Straßen- und Gebäudenamen" class="link icon placemark"></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>